{"tid":1495343,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"我係一個地盤佬，細個時嘅夢想係漫畫家。","createTime":"2019-08-22T04:28:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T13:27:21.000Z","uid":216800,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c4ef806eddb4248621684536dd3bfb13dfda0c26","tid":1495343,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T04:28:15.000Z","msg":"今日因工作要去港大做野 黎之前已經做咗兩單<br />\n時間關係阿頭話食飯先<br />\n我打開銀包 得返45蚊<br />\n<br />\n7號出糧 交家用交房租交水電煤 得返3000鬆啲<br />\n但到今日得返45蚊...<br />\n啲錢去晒邊？<br />\n發夢 課金 打boss    當然係被boss打嗰個..<br />\n做得勇武派 少不了嘅係減低受傷嘅裝備<br />\n但一套靚嘅防裝都唔平 保護自己嘅野唔慳得<br />\n出去發夢都係一日先食一餐<br />\n有時食到一半 防暴已經推進<br />\n即刻食多一大啖就要抌低個叉雞飯<br />\n含住好大啖嘅飯 一路咀嚼一路衝去前線幫拖<br />\n仲要噴住飯叫大家快啲走<br />\n哩種辛酸 我義無反顧<br />\n<br />\n講返轉頭<br />\n今日早上有義士朋友過數還返700蚊比我<br />\n打開銀包得返45蚊果時 終於可以去食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n果45蚊由禮拜一留到今日<br />\n即係意味著我無食正餐3日<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">每日都係食鄰居送嘅麵包<br />\n佢做麵包鋪 每次都送一大袋 唔係佢我都唔知點過</span><br />\n我叫咗個叉雞飯連芬達<br />\n坐低一路食 <br />\n啲眼淚一路流<br />\n我真係好希望哩一兩個月以黎 自己真係發緊夢<br />\n但哩個就係現實<br />\n我上前線 我都會驚 我都怕痛<br />\n自己仲要鍾意畫公仔 <br />\n打斷咗隻手就咁一世 再揸唔穩支筆<br />\n但我出去嘅原因係因為我都有下一代<br />\n因為上一代唔理唔爭取 <br />\n要由我地哩代人黎流住<span style=\"color: red;\">血</span>爭取<br />\n我唔想下一代都係咁<br />\n再經歷咁多恐怖 致殘 被消失<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S18sohL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS18sohL.jpg&h=18bbb1df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"993f650ef05fd3ac9fa028c64a42c327aa062532","tid":1495343,"uid":263772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T04:32:17.000Z","msg":"加油，我戶口得返100<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53bbf8a754d2ba65ec585bf063f38f933ec60bb7","tid":1495343,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"993f650ef05fd3ac9fa028c64a42c327aa062532","tid":1495343,"uid":263772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T04:32:17.000Z","msg":"加油，我戶口得返100<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T04:45:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加油，共勉之"},{"pid":"6852ecb639305d58ab3f2cd8c107e2b43edabea0","tid":1495343,"uid":263772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T12:58:45.000Z","msg":"唉，巴打呢排點，好撚辛苦，出去出得好辛苦，好撚大壓力，又窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f258801594b92e7904c776143baae823b669f353","tid":1495343,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6852ecb639305d58ab3f2cd8c107e2b43edabea0","tid":1495343,"uid":263772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T12:58:45.000Z","msg":"唉，巴打呢排點，好撚辛苦，出去出得好辛苦，好撚大壓力，又窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T15:29:03.000Z","msg":"我都係喺周圍徘徊，唔敢去太遠<br />\n啱啱喺台灣返香港 都係女朋友比晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ba431703a83feb9ee2ce09dc818811360fc4fd0","tid":1495343,"uid":263772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f258801594b92e7904c776143baae823b669f353","tid":1495343,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6852ecb639305d58ab3f2cd8c107e2b43edabea0","tid":1495343,"uid":263772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T12:58:45.000Z","msg":"唉，巴打呢排點，好撚辛苦，出去出得好辛苦，好撚大壓力，又窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T15:29:03.000Z","msg":"我都係喺周圍徘徊，唔敢去太遠<br />\n啱啱喺台灣返香港 都係女朋友比晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T08:01:47.000Z","msg":"有女朋友真好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，星期四又要返工<img src=\"/assets/fac